data.description: House In Port Charlotte - in the perfect, quiet location, close to schools, shopping with a grocery store and shopping plaza, many restaurants nearby,  and a short drive up to Charlotte Beach.    NO RENTAL RESTRICTIONS.  No HOA. NO FLOODING.    This is a 1,232 square foot house on a 10,399 sq/ft lot with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, one car garage, city water and sewer.   BRAND NEW ROOF!  One of two lanais is completely closed, has an AC, and can be used as an additional room/room for guests.  Schedule your private showing today.
